<th scope="row" id="fileinfotpl_src">Source
</th>
<td>
<p><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20110526220856/http://sipi.usc.edu/database/database.php?volume=misc&amp;image=12">The USC-SIPI image database</a>
